name: Experiment Or Die #45
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The last couple pieces have been about transformation and where 1 piece an be taken from each day to the next. The Georgia Aquarium is the largest one in the United States and I forgot that I had plenty of these jellyfish snaps from the very first time we visited like 10 years ago. Every time one of these creatures moves it seems to morph into something new. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
